<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSmith2006">Smith, Douglas V. (2006). <i>Carrier Battles: Command Decision in Harm's Way</i>. U.S. Naval Institute Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1591147948" class="internal">ISBN 1591147948</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Carrier+Battles%3A+Command+Decision+in+Harm%27s+Way&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Douglas+V.&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Douglas+V.&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.pub=U.S.+Naval+Institute+Press&amp;rft.isbn=1591147948&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Battle_of_Midway"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSmith2007"><a href="/wiki/Peter_C._Smith" title="Peter C. Smith">Smith, Peter C.</a> (2007). <i>Midway Dauntless Victory; Fresh perspectives on America's Seminal Naval Victory of 1942</i>. Barnsley, UK: Pen &amp; Sword Maritime. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1844155838" class="internal">ISBN 184415583-8</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Midway+Dauntless+Victory%3B+Fresh+perspectives+on+America%27s+Seminal+Naval+Victory+of+1942&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter+C.&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Peter+C.&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.place=Barnsley%2C+UK&amp;rft.pub=Pen+%26+Sword+Maritime&amp;rft.isbn=184415583-8&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Battle_of_Midway"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> Detailed study of battle, from planning to the effects on WWII</li>
